Proof that the scale is nothing but a number.  Amazing job Staci!! - Repost @holisticliving_4life .  Scale weight let's take a hot minute to talk about it. I'm scrolling through pictures and come across the one on the left... hated that picture. I looked like the damn Pillsbury dough boy
That picture on the right... I'm still thick but
there's muscle and definition starting! Here's a secret... I weigh 16 pounds MORE on the right but look and feel so much better! The scale doesn't define you! That scale does not measure your worth or your size! For all the people weighing themselves religiously because we have all been taught that our weight defines us, remember... The scale doesn't define you!!!
Oh and for the love of life do the scary shit and post the pictures, you never know who you inspire along the way . 
.
